fields.category_description:
All that remains, in the end, are memories Everything is lost in the end but the best memoirs.
Enter to explore more and make sure you get one for yourself.
Be proud of the legacy you own.

We all love to be in the pair.So we have something special for you people wherein we have clubbed for you some of the best products taking care of the budget.
We bet you will love our combo products.

Searching for best outfits??? 
Well the best ones are searching for ya! Grab the tees to sport that SWAG you definitely got.Top the chart of style and let the world know the other side of you.! 
Well we have something better
in store for ya!!!Dress up well….

Your wardrobe is incomplete without these cool accessories.
We Know you do possess the latest gadgets. Try out these ritzy accessories.
We bet these would add extra swag to your everyday cool attire as you walk down your college lane.

fields.name: Classy White Coffee mug
fields.description:
Memories as they say need to be preserved.
We bring to you those memories in every sip of your coffee.Just in case you feel proud of the place you belong, this mug will serve your purpose.
Coffee time is a nice time, let’s make it the best one.

fields.name: The Legacy Coffee Mug
fields.description:
What if I told you that every sip of your coffee will remind you of your Alma Mater. That the word JAMIAN itself will call you down the memory lane…. 
Just one more time, let nostalgia grip you as you hold in your hands coffee mug. The “black beauty”.

fields.name: QR Tee + Athletic Sipper
fields.description:
Okay!!! So we will suggest you to get the best of both worlds. 
A cool T-shirt and sipper will complete your idea of a gypsy traveller. Grab the two at minimal prices and get ready to welcome summers in style.

fields.name: Athletic Grey Sipper
fields.description:
With Summers round the corner,you won't really wanna ease off your mood of grabbing these  Athletic Sipper. Make sure you possess the best...
Well these sippers are the new "cool" in the town to quench your thirst.

fields.name: UpTurn Grey Hoodie with logo
fields.description:
Brace yourself this winter in the interesting hue of grey.
Make your morning jogs a bit sleek and stylish.
Make the most of the snowy season and deck yourself out in
these cool hoodies. Need more reasons to go out in the chilly nights!!And as they say, “Grey is often more interesting than black and
white.”

fields.name: Quantify Blue Hoodie
fields.description:
“Style is a way to say who you are without having to speak”. 
The measuring scale with the red mark on the 33.3 would definitely make you feel that you are worth than just the passing marks. 
Make your statement and flaunt your Jamian side. This winter let the world know that “YOU BELONG HERE!!!”Team up this classy blue hoodie with any light jeans or chinos and have the confidence that you are the best.

fields.name: MI Black Collar Tee
fields.description:
Get this comfy Grey MI  polo T-shirt from Roba Square that makes a relaxing casual wear.
 Made from cotton, this simple T-shirt offers unmatched comfort, no wonder it will become your favourite soon. Pair it with jeans and casual sneakers.
Carry the swagger and flaunt your style statement as you rush through the college hours.Make sure you grab it before your friend does.

Pair it with jeans and casual sneakers.Carry the swagger and flaunt your style statement as you rush through  the college hours.Make sure you grab it before your friend does.

fields.name: Round Neck QR Code Tee
fields.description:
For once just wear it without any reason. And that’s when you’ll be at your best. 
No need for reasons always. Add this t-shirt to your frequent wears and you are ready to carry that casual look be it the hectic weekdays or much awaited weekend outings.
Even Mondays won’t seem a big deal if you start your week with these casual t-shirts and a pair of fitted denim. Break the budget dilemma and grab these tees.
Just team these with your denims and there you are…ready to flaunt. Where did you see the attires that actually speak for ya! Well, it does so here.
So, why not wear what you literally feel. Sounds interesting ha!!!

fields.name: Unchained Backpack
fields.description:
The Unchained Backpacks is not just about looks, though there's plenty of that.
While this pack makes a statement as you cruise through the streets on two feet or two wheels, it's about features like the main compartment laptop sleeve that fits 15-inch laptops, or the zippered mesh valuables pocket and the side water bottle pocket make carrying everything a breeze.
It's also about comfort because when this backpack is loaded down, the quilted back panel and lightweight shoulder straps help ease the load.
The Unchained Backpack is the whole package.So go ahead, show off your swagger with the Unchained Backpack.

fields.name: Sipper + Backpack
fields.description:
Its time to explore the sporty as well as the traveller side in  you.
The sipper clubbed with the  the backpacks will make sure you cover length as well as the breadth of life without getting tired as you also possess the athletic sipper to quench your thirst.
And it wont cost you much just in case you wanna grab it.

fields.name: Sassy Tote + Black Mug
fields.description:
Ladies, what if you could afford a funky tote bag and a supercool coffee mug at a price for which you could barely afford one of these elsewhere.
Well, you need to stop wondering and order the combo right away.  This is what we call “value for money”.

fields.name: Sassy Canvas Tote Bags
fields.description:
GIRLS!!!! It’s high time you funk up your outings and shopping sprees with these trendy tote bags.You won’t really want to miss these bags out.
They work to complete your perfect cool look. Add these chichi tote bags to your collection of accessories and be ready to flaunt your style your way.

fields.name: Detained Tee + Black Mug
fields.description:
Create an interesting pair of gifts with a funky T-shirt and the alluring coffee mug. 
Your book nerd friend will love you for this. 
Gift it to a friend or just make the use of available offer for yourself.  Whatever, you won’t find a reason to miss out on this combo

fields.name: Detained Round Neck Tee
fields.description:
Let your funky tees do the talking. Create your own style statement Once you have got these T-shirts all you need is a pair of denim and a bit of attitude. 
A dose of confidence comes free with your attire.Stay wild stay you.  Meet the real you with these T-shirts. BTW, did you reach that “75% attendance” mark??!!
Next time make sure you have that 75%.
